metadata.name: Vintage night out
metadata.description:
I have dreams of our red car,
and the downpour that turned into drizzle that night.
The smell of the rain; and the vibrant lights;
blurred by your laughter
and the drops kissing the windshield all night.

Our song played a smile, and the streets glowed for a while,
We caught glimpses of curious eyes,
but we didn't stop, we just drove by...

DETAILS: 
The vintage car with venetian blinds is COMPLETELY FINGER PAINTED. Each and every stroke leads to the story.
Original Artwork
size: 30*40 inches
medium: Oils
